sequenceDiagram
    participant P as Publisher
    participant B as Broker
    participant S as Subscriber

    Note over P,S: QoS 0: Fire-and-Forget

    P->>B: PUBLISH (QoS=0, topic="sensor/temp", payload="25.3")
    Note right of P: Packet ID なし<br/>確認応答なし
    B->>S: PUBLISH (QoS=0, topic="sensor/temp", payload="25.3")
    Note over P,S: メッセージロスの可能性あり

    Note over P,S: ────────────────────────

    Note over P,S: QoS 1: At Least Once

    P->>B: PUBLISH (QoS=1, id=1, topic="sensor/temp", payload="26.1")
    B->>P: PUBACK (id=1)
    Note right of B: Broker は Packet ID=1 の<br/>PUBLISH を受信確認

    B->>S: PUBLISH (QoS=1, id=100, topic="sensor/temp", payload="26.1")
    Note right of B: Subscriber への配信時は<br/>Broker が新しい Packet ID を割り当て
    S->>B: PUBACK (id=100)

    Note over P,S: ────────────────────────

    Note over P,S: QoS 1: 再送シナリオ

    P->>B: PUBLISH (QoS=1, id=2, topic="alert/fire", payload="detected")
    Note over P: PUBACK が来ない...<br/>タイムアウト
    P->>B: PUBLISH (QoS=1, id=2, DUP=1, topic="alert/fire", payload="detected")
    B->>P: PUBACK (id=2)
    Note over P,S: DUP=1 により再送パケットと識別可能
